                     <interp inst="t18121028-73-off409" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18121028-73-off409" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18121028-73-cd410" type="crimeDate">23d of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18121028-73-off409 t18121028-73-cd410"></join>, a watch, value 5 l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18121028-73-victim807" type="victimName">
